      "id": "f548dba6-809f-4d30-90d6-439b5f4f1a2c",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Forecasting student success can help develop specific interventions that address student needs. Authors identify the 3 types of features normally used in predictive modelling: demographics, academic background and behavioral data. ",
