      "id": "3aa8bb8f-4def-4aa1-9444-e7d5cffe817f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors procceed to compare the performance of multipe ML algorithms on the task of predicting student performance - score on final examinations. Logistic Regression achieved the best scores at predicting the exact final grade - 69% for students who passed and 89% for students who failed.",
